{"type": "article", "id": 38079, "title": "灵感转瞬即逝？试试这支录音笔｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-02-22T23:17:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 37926, "name": "Capra Designs"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 174, "image": "img/article/article_show/201702222243465gUipNuL7VdbhIfn.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Seastone</h3><p>虽然很多人都知道“好记性不如烂笔头”的道理，但实际情况往往是我们都不能保证灵感乍现时手边必定准备了记录用的工具。为了不让那些珍贵的想法在手忙脚乱找笔时烟消云散，来自美国的 Seastone 设计团队研发了这款智能录音工具，可以夹在衣领上使用。一旦你有记下什么的需要，只要轻轻一按它就会开始录音，完成后将自动把这段音频和对应的文档同步到手机 app 中，之后你可以再把内容分享到自己惯用的笔记软件内。即便暂时处于无法连接手机的情况，只要它恢复连接就能自动更新上传。目前 Seastone 可以识别出包括中文在内的 11 种语言，并支持简/繁两种文字导出。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/835264493/senstone-the-intelligent-wearable-voice-recorder\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 100 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222224430gQ5pICDdzwhx1WoM.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.740625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222224428rOJ64mItD5aYdL7K.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.747917\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222224427ZMdlLa3kVCSrgn9G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222224427j2xGIyqwZ6RApvg1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222224427Rt9PEeDKUmAu0Y1j.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222224428ECyBoceMqb7OPQJH.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.657353\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>HEY by House of Haptics</h3><p>尽管身处两地，我们和所爱之人的沟通往往不再像过去那样受限，但总有一些时刻会让我们更向往语言之外的肢体接触。由荷兰初创公司 House of Haptics 开发的 HEY 就是一款能够传递心意的智能腕带，两根手环通过蓝牙和手机 app 相连后，只要一方按压自己的手环，另一方的手环就会接受到信号，并模拟出一种号称是具有真人触碰感的紧握动作，而不是机械式的震动。为了避免误触，在使用时必须同时按压到两个感应点才会触发。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1596731227/hey-a-revolutionary-bracelet-that-sends-touch-over\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，两根腕带的套装最低价为 74 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222224450NOKl2kqZcXJBwzyT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.585294\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222224451C2WZDF5H8dIgS1UA.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.559375\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222224451gBGnVZj6fomCKueR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.779412\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222224452xjNPFu3sYa7KXr5E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222224452kyXQ8Le02AEjt3dM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.110294\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Playful Base by Root Co.</h3><p>参与野营或是探险这类户外活动，少不了各式各样的装备，背包也因此难以减负。最近来自日本箱根的设计公司 Root Co. 就以智能手机为灵感，设计了这款多功能的户外装备 Playful Base。号称具有 IP65 级防尘防水性能的它既是水瓶，又能当作扬声器以及灯具使用，当水瓶倒入不同颜色的饮料时，灯光的颜色也会因此改变。加上配套的防水充电器，它还能变身成移动电源。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.makuake.com/project/playfulbase/\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，单独购买水瓶的最低价为 4320 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222224513nlACa3EL6cYbyoid.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.813008\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222224513lu1dhRvTzH345yJQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.716667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017022222451337oVt1zC5PwvUu0c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.716667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222224514NQspxct0TzLr9qUu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.716667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222224513zQBX3ryAU2HYkwMF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.716667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222224515dIvQ7w5UNuGqRn41.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.066667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Aurora eco resin vases by Capra Designs</h3><p><a href=\"http://capradesigns.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Capra Designs</a> 是一个来自澳大利亚墨尔本的手工艺品牌，在制作名为 Aurora 的花盆系列时，联合创始人 Bianca Lambert 发现有很多被当做废料处理的水性树脂就这么被垒在了一边。意识到这些废料也可以有用武之地的 Lambert 将它们收集起来，创作了一批式样独一无二的花瓶，不仅有着随性的美感，还进一步减少了制作过程中产生的浪费。这是它们的<a href=\"http://capradesigns.com/vases/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价从 79 澳元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222224538ClKkvnp3m2Z7rqae.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222224539MwFjuYxBas3pOEUI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.359259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702222245396mfaWSeX3KiHx5gM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702222245398i0Y2CB76EvaKmxg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.637037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222224538LSEMfjXdNW0KgiQr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.287037\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Argentinian Pesos by Gilda Martini &amp; Gabriela Lubiano</h3><p>位于南美洲的阿根廷是一个生物多样性大国，有记录的动植物物种数在各个类别都排名世界前列。为了致敬这个特殊的生态系统，平面设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gildamartini\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gilda Martini</a> 和 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/GabiLubiano\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gabriela Lubiano</a> 以当地动植物为主题重新设计了阿根廷的货币比索，并在背面配上了它们的栖息地。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222224628KSPDg3yL9GNXcrYl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.100000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222224628Qf5DGuP67NYK8yEz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.132222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222224628kbJDBOH4sTGeqdEo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.091111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222224628tApM7TWs8igIHDlh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.185556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222224629YBLNZv0awK3yutHR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.216667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222224629QLSDTkN0ReO3jWyw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.136667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Paradise. Gourmet-club by Sergii Artemov</h3><p>在呈现咖啡浓度这个细节上，乌克兰平面设计师 Sergii Artemov 为 Paradise. Gourmet-club 的浓缩咖啡系列打造的包装选择了一个相当讨巧的主题：月相。从 20% 到 80% 的四个浓度，分别以眉月到满月的镀银插画表示，和简单的数字相比，能让消费者更直观地感受到喝下这些咖啡的效果。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222224719aGFD6AiSHoZupwYW.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.462000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222224720LmChANxJWjS7bf0n.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.838000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222224720drGfDxewo1qJ5us6.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.838000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702222247215xBTpXaAnvIOM9ys.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.837333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222224721hZT5mSoUDfWiy2EO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.838000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}